in \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13461,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/08\/prefer-akhirah-over-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":40092,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Prefer afterlife that remains forever","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever loves his worldly life will suffer in his Hereafter, and whoever loves his Hereafter will suffer in his worldly life. Thus, prefer what is everlasting over what will vanish.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 709 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38273,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/28\/root-of-all-evil\/","url_meta":{"origin":40092,"position":5},"title":"Hasan on Dunya: Love of worldly life is root of all evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cLove of the worldly life is the head of every sin.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 9 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0